Brand Founder Identity Map

A structured exercise to define the founder’s story and emotional foundation.

## 1. Founder Questions

What personal experience shaped your worldview?

What problem did you see that others ignored?

What internal conflict led you to start this brand?

What do you stand for?

What will you never compromise?

What transformation did you undergo that mirrors your customer's?

## 2. Emotional DNA

Fill the following:

Core Emotion

Triggering Moment

Founder Truth

Brand Manifesto Sentence

## 3. Identity Summary

“As a founder, I believe _______, and I created this brand to ________ because I am committed to ________.”
